{"tid":1394834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗入瑪麗醫院臨床腫瘤科電療部，健康成疑","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:17:04.000Z","uid":177556,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6adc47fb14523b8c3f53b23d89798fdca1b22c55","tid":1394834,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"「反送中」運動持續，特首林鄭月娥下台的消息不絕，不過《蘋果》發現，作為特區政府第二把交椅、隨時署任特首之位的張建宗，近日多次出入瑪麗醫院臨床腫瘤科電療部，健康成疑。據了解，張建宗7月初起已須逢周一至周五、每日到瑪麗醫院接受電療，至今已持續一個月。政務司司長辦公室表示，張建宗的鼻腔內有一微小囊腫，需接受療程，但稱情況輕微，不影響執行職務。有立法會議員促張建宗進一步交代病情，釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190801&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59887400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190801%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59887400&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3556b8fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190801%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59887400&h=e0f2c34a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190801&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59887400</a>"},{"pid":"7cc20f61969e89043300a9995c19e3da81174d3a","tid":1394834,"uid":175976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"快喇快喇"},{"pid":"d18456364d138b5922fa0748786c37477676b32e","tid":1394834,"uid":36049,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"奇拿再黎次皇天擊殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8193960d3244afb99f9c4f7080161f26b9acfde5","tid":1394834,"uid":63950,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03589b26a17d683244d69d772f72913c72b343db","tid":1394834,"uid":178791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201